00:00:04.257 --> 00:00:12.570 align:middle line:90%


00:00:12.570 --> 00:00:19.370 align:middle line:84%
>>"Eastern Wisdom and Modern
Life" with Alan W. Watts.

00:00:19.370 --> 00:00:21.990 align:middle line:90%


00:00:21.990 --> 00:00:28.990 align:middle line:84%
